thread.title: Little Rudolphs Club
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Little Rudolphs Club

author: Little Rudolphs Club
title: Little Rudolphs Club
text:
Hi everybody,
The prices are competitive and most of the time a little cheaper but the free delivery offer is outstanding as i bought my items on the phone at 2pm and it got delivered at 10am next day. Didn't have to wait until afternoon run (3-4pm).
Staff are friendly and wil help you to make the right choice at your best interest in mind.
Customer satisfaction for me is excellent as they deliver on their promised.
Thank you
